Package net.cinnom.nanocuckoo.encode

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StringEncoder
    Provides functionality for encoding a String into a byte array.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASCIIEncoder
    StringEncoder for encoding ASCII Strings.
    HexEncoder
    StringEncoder for encoding Hexadecimal Strings.
    UnsafeEncoder
    StringEncoder that will directly copy char[] to byte[] using Unsafe.
    UTF16LEEncoder
    StringEncoder for encoding UTF-16 Little Endian Strings.
    UTF8Encoder
    StringEncoder for encoding UTF-8 Strings.
